OL,3,CEx-Chief Minister's proposition gets
OL,4,Cno backing, except her own vote
OL,6,FDeputy Sir Philip Bailhache called the
OL,7,Fplan "entirely unworkable".
OL,9,FThe Housing Minister, Deputy Sam
OL,10,FMezec, commended Deputy Moore for
OL,11,Flooking to change the electoral
OL,12,Fsystem, which he described as
OL,13,F"inadequate".
OL,15,FHowever, he concluded that the
OL,16,Fproposition "had more holes than a
OL,17,Fsieve" and "would lead ultimately to
OL,18,Fchaos".
