OL,3,CEx-Chief Minister's proposition gets
OL,4,Cno backing, except her own vote
OL,6,FDeputy Philip Ozouf said, "Unlike
OL,7,Fother members, I'm a Jerseyman and I
OL,8,Frespect Jersey traditions".
OL,10,FAfter a number of opposing speeches,
OL,11,FDeputy Montfort Tadier added, "Do we
OL,12,Fneed any more reasons not to vote for
OL,13,Fthis?"
OL,15,FBefore the vote, Deputy Moore said,
OL,16,F"If nothing else, this proposition has
OL,17,Fgot people talking - not us in here,
OL,18,Fbut those people outside who we
OL,19,Frepresent.
